    "To shed light on this challenge, the researchers posed the following questions:• what are the different types of AI-driven cyberattacks?• what strategies and techniques can be used to mitigate AI-driven cyberattacks?",
    "• what are the motivations of AI-empowered cyber attackers?",
    "• what are the potential societal impacts of AI-driven cyberattacks?",
